      <title>Hexo魔改：首页轮播组件测试</title>
      <link href="/post/44772.html"/>
      <url>/post/44772.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hexo魔改：首页轮播组件测试"><a href="#Hexo魔改：首页轮播组件测试" class="headerlink" title="Hexo魔改：首页轮播组件测试"></a>Hexo魔改：首页轮播组件测试</h1><h2 id="1-效果预览"><a href="#1-效果预览" class="headerlink" title="1. 效果预览"></a>1. 效果预览</h2><p><a href="https://gitee.com/wyw_0227/picture-bed/raw/master/Hexo/202409041923547.png">https://gitee.com/wyw_0227/picture-bed/raw/master/Hexo/202409041923547.png</a></p><h2 id="2-教程"><a href="#2-教程" class="headerlink" title="2. 教程"></a>2. 教程</h2><h3 id="第一步：安装插件"><a href="#第一步：安装插件" class="headerlink" title="第一步：安装插件"></a>第一步：安装插件</h3><p>在博客根目录下打开终端，运行以下指令：</p><p>bash复制</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-butterfly-swiper --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="第二步：配置站点"><a href="#第二步：配置站点" class="headerlink" title="第二步：配置站点"></a>第二步：配置站点</h3><p>在站点配置文件 <code>_config.yml</code> 中添加以下配置信息：</p><p>yaml复制</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">swiper:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">priority:</span> <span class="number">5</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable_page:</span> <span class="string">/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">timemode:</span> <span class="string">date</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">layout:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">id</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">recent</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">-posts</span>    <span class="attr">index:</span> <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">default_descr:</span> <span class="string">想一个默认描述好难的！</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">swiper_css:</span> <span class="string">https://npm.elemecdn.com/hexo-butterfly-swiper/lib/swiper.min.css</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">swiper_js:</span> <span class="string">https://npm.elemecdn.com/hexo-butterfly-swiper/lib/swiper.min.js</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">custom_css:</span> <span class="string">https://npm.elemecdn.com/hexo-butterfly-swiper/lib/swiperstyle.css</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">custom_js:</span> <span class="string">https://npm.elemecdn.com/hexo-butterfly-swiper/lib/swiper_init.js</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="第三步：自定义配置参数"><a href="#第三步：自定义配置参数" class="headerlink" title="第三步：自定义配置参数"></a>第三步：自定义配置参数</h3><ul><li><strong>priority</strong>：过滤器优先级，数值越小，执行越早，默认为10。</li><li><strong>enable</strong>：是否开启轮播组件（必填）。</li><li><strong>enable_page</strong>：应用地址，主页填 <code>/</code>，分类页面填 <code>/categories/</code>，所有页面填 <code>all</code>，默认为 <code>all</code>。</li><li><strong>timemode</strong>：<code>date</code> 显示创建日期，<code>updated</code> 显示更新日期，默认为 <code>date</code>。</li><li><strong>layout.type</strong>：挂载容器类型，<code>id</code> 或 <code>class</code>，默认为 <code>id</code>。</li><li><strong>layout.name</strong>：挂载容器名称（必填）。</li><li><strong>layout.index</strong>：当 <code>layout.type</code> 为 <code>class</code> 时，用来确认排在第几位。</li><li><strong>default_descr</strong>：默认文章描述。</li></ul><h3 id="第四步：在文章的-Front-Matter-中使用"><a href="#第四步：在文章的-Front-Matter-中使用" class="headerlink" title="第四步：在文章的 Front-Matter 中使用"></a>第四步：在文章的 Front-Matter 中使用</h3><p>在文章的 Front-Matter 中添加以下内容：</p><p>yaml复制</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">文章标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="string">创建日期</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">updated:</span> <span class="string">更新日期</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">cover:</span> <span class="string">文章封面</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">文章描述</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">swiper_index:</span> <span class="number">1</span> <span class="comment"># 置顶轮播图顺序，非负整数，数字越大越靠前</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-参考链接"><a href="#3-参考链接" class="headerlink" title="3. 参考链接"></a>3. 参考链接</h2><ul><li><a href="https://dasi.net.cn/posts/5f3e08e1/">原文链接</a>：感谢原作者的分享，更多细节可以参考原文。</li></ul><hr><h3 id="转载声明"><a href="#转载声明" class="headerlink" title="转载声明"></a>转载声明</h3><p>本文转载自 <a href="https://dasi.net.cn/posts/5f3e08e1/">原文链接</a>，版权归原作者所有。如有任何问题，请联系原作者。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
